data.description: MOVE IN READY home in Lake of the Woods UNDER $300K with a PARTIAL LAKE VIEW!!!!  Home boasts significant updates including a NEW ROOF in  2015, Windows replaced in 2013, Newer Siding, Carpet, and Paint.  Rooms are of Generous Size.  Excellent access to the wrap-around back porch through the kitchen as well as through the oversized Laundry Room,  Huge Shed out back for storage or a great workspace fully equipped with its own power supply & box. The home has a Circular Driveway with overflow space offering TONS of parking.  ONLY 240 Ft from Cornwallis Beach!  Fully Gated Lake of the Woods Community is just a short drive to Fredericksburg and Culpeper and Amenity Filled!  Lake, Beaches, Pools, 18 Hole Golf Course, Equestrian Center, Multiple, Restaurants, and more!
